{"tid":592024,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴獲讚：世界最佳中場 五年內能奪金球獎","createTime":"2018-03-14T02:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T13:17:48.000Z","uid":166908,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d18fb2750a629d6ba44fe8bd228607db7e661dde","tid":592024,"uid":166908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"　　《每日郵報》報導，馬迪爾盛讚曼聯隊友普巴是世界最佳中場，並相信他能在未來五年內拿到金球獎。<br />\n<br />\n　　普巴之前因為糟糕的狀態淪為後備，他和摩連奴的關係也遭到質疑，不過曼聯隊友對他的評價依然非常高。<br />\n<br />\n　　曼聯兼法國隊友馬迪爾表示：「我認為普巴很可能是世界最佳中場。他的精神非常強大，也很自信。他是個大傢伙，拿球技術出色，而且很有耐力。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「他還年輕，還有很大的提升空間，能夠變得更加出色。如果他繼續進步，我認為他將在未來五年內贏得金球獎。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#dog1 #dog2"},{"pid":"bae62937f4d4963115785a54e590e881af61ae96","tid":592024,"uid":145365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:23:13.000Z","msg":"魔迪卻奧斯都未拎 拎呢隻nigga 黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a27b24f9025307a4d9deb976cbfe4eb366fa6d0","tid":592024,"uid":33789,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:34:00.000Z","msg":"呢隻黑奴幫我奶袋底都唔夠班呀"},{"pid":"5d4ef97cdf0575e6a60a2a157d134e3b1ab3d37d","tid":592024,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d956e051fa2c40489330ce137d55d1977b0fe4ed","tid":592024,"uid":6577,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魔迪卻奧斯都未拎 拎呢隻nigga 黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係 摩迪 卻老 小白 施華 迪布尼 計埋簡迪 頭5都未輪到條力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d993e55c196d30a21c69a75d7bf38c4636f7cf16","tid":592024,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc